    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 1,
      "id": "middleware-title",
      "x": 720,
      "y": 450,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 25,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "🧠 APPLICATION LAYER (FastAPI Middleware)",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "groupIds": ["middleware"],
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 1,
      "id": "middleware-details",
      "x": 720,
      "y": 485,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 290,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "🟢 MVP Core Components:\n\n1️⃣ Request Handler\n   → Validate input, generate correlation ID\n\n2️⃣ RAG Retrieval Engine\n   → Query embedding → ChromaDB search (top 5)\n   → Re-rank results → Format context\n\n3️⃣ Agent Orchestrator\n   → Decide: RAG only, Tools, or Both\n   → Multi-turn conversation management\n\n4️⃣ Smart Router (LLM Judge)\n   → Analyze query complexity\n   → Select tier: local/lakeshore/cloud\n   → Fallback logic: Ollama → vLLM → OpenAI\n\n5️⃣ Tool Executor (SLURM)\n   → check_queue_status(), get_job_details()\n   → estimate_wait_time()\n\n6️⃣ Cost Tracker → PostgreSQL logging\n\n7️⃣ Response Builder\n   → LLM answer + citations + cost metadata",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "groupIds": ["middleware"],
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },

