      "x": 720,
      "y": 895,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 120,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Unified LLM Interface:\n• Local: Ollama (llama2, mistral, codellama)\n• Campus: vLLM on Lakeshore GPU (70B+ models)\n• Cloud: OpenAI, Claude, Gemini\n\nFeatures: Token counting, cost tracking,\nautomated retries, provider error handling",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "groupIds": ["litellm"],
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },

