    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 1,
      "id": "rag-title",
      "x": 120,
      "y": 690,
      "width": 510,
      "height": 25,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "🔍 RAG INFRASTRUCTURE (Critical MVP)",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "groupIds": ["rag"],
      "strokeColor": "#e67700",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 1,
      "id": "rag-details",
      "x": 120,
      "y": 725,
      "width": 510,
      "height": 290,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "📦 MinIO (S3 Storage)\n  • Original documents (PDFs, DOCX)\n  • UIC policies, handbooks, course materials\n\n🔢 ChromaDB (Vector Database)\n  • Document embeddings (50k chunks at start)\n  • Semantic search with cosine similarity\n  • Collection: 'uic_documents'\n\n🧮 Embedding Service\n  • Model: sentence-transformers/all-MiniLM-L6-v2\n  • OR OpenAI text-embedding-3-small\n  • Cached in Redis\n\n✂️ Document Processing Pipeline\n  • Upload API: POST /v1/documents/upload\n  • Text extraction: PyPDF2, python-docx\n  • Chunking: 512 tokens, 50 overlap\n  • Indexing: Async background workers\n\n📊 Metadata (PostgreSQL)\n  • Document index, upload timestamps\n  • Chunk mappings, source attribution",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "groupIds": ["rag"],
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },

    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "version": 1,
      "id": "data-layer-box",
      "x": 100,
      "y": 1080,
      "width": 550,
      "height": 250,
      "strokeColor": "#5f3dc4",
      "backgroundColor": "#e5dbff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 3,
