      "roundness": {"type": 3}
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 1,
      "id": "monitoring-title",
      "x": 720,
      "y": 1230,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 25,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "📊 OBSERVABILITY LAYER (CRITICAL MVP!)",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "groupIds": ["monitoring"],
      "strokeColor": "#c92a2a",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 1,
      "id": "monitoring-details",
      "x": 720,
      "y": 1265,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 150,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "🟢 MVP: Basic Monitoring (MOVED FROM PHASE 4!)\n  • Python logging to stdout (correlation IDs)\n  • Request/response logs, error stack traces\n  • Health checks: /health endpoint\n  • Simple metrics in PostgreSQL\n    (request count, costs, latency, error rates)\n\n🟡 Phase 3: Full Stack\n  • Prometheus - Metrics collection\n  • Grafana - Dashboards & visualization\n  • Loki - Centralized logging\n  • Alerting - PagerDuty/Slack notifications\n\n🟣 Phase 4: Enterprise (Splunk, Jaeger tracing, APM)",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "groupIds": ["monitoring"],
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },

    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 1,
      "id": "legend-title",
      "x": 1400,
      "y": 100,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 30,
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Implementation Phases",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fontWeight": "bold"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 1,
      "id": "legend-content",
      "x": 1400,
      "y": 140,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 160,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "🟢 MVP (Weeks 1-4)\n   Core functionality\n   $231/month\n\n🔵 Phase 2 (Weeks 5-8)\n   Authentication + SSO\n   $535/month\n\n🟡 Phase 3 (Months 3-4)\n   Scalability + MCP Tools\n   $1,142/month\n\n🟣 Phase 4 (Months 5-6)\n   Enterprise features\n   $2,257/month",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },

    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 1,
      "id": "flow-notes-title",
      "x": 1400,
      "y": 350,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 30,
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Request Flow",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fontWeight": "bold"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 1,
      "id": "flow-notes-content",
      "x": 1400,
      "y": 390,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 300,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "1. User query →\n   Gateway (auth, rate limit)\n\n2. Middleware receives query\n   ↓\n3. RAG Retrieval Engine\n   • Embed query\n   • Search ChromaDB\n   • Get top 5 chunks\n   ↓\n4. Agent Orchestrator\n   • Decide: RAG/Tools/Both\n   • Check if SLURM tools needed\n   ↓\n5. Smart Router\n   • Analyze complexity\n   • Select tier (local/GPU/cloud)\n   ↓\n6. LiteLLM Gateway\n   • Route to selected model\n   • Fallback if needed\n   ↓\n7. Response Builder\n   • LLM answer + citations\n   • Cost metadata\n   • Log to PostgreSQL\n   ↓\n8. Stream to user",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },

