      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "🟢 MVP: Direct SLURM Functions\n  • check_queue_status()\n  • get_job_details(job_id)\n  • estimate_wait_time(partition)\n  • No MCP yet\n\n🟡 Phase 3: MCP Tool Gateway\n  • LDAP search tool\n  • Library catalog search\n  • Campus resources\n  • ABAC policy enforcement\n  • Secrets in Vault (never in apps)\n\n🟣 Phase 4:\n  • Custom tool registry\n  • Multi-agent collaboration\n  • Tool usage analytics",
