      "height": 300,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "MVP: $231/month\n  • Docker containers (free)\n  • PostgreSQL (free)\n  • Redis (free)\n  • MinIO (free)\n  • ChromaDB (free)\n  • Ollama (free, uses existing HW)\n  • Let's Encrypt SSL (free)\n  • Cloud APIs: $231/month\n    (pay-as-you-go fallback)\n\nPhase 3: $1,142/month\n  • + NGINX load balancer\n  • + Redis Cluster\n  • + PostgreSQL replicas\n  • + Prometheus/Grafana\n  • + RabbitMQ\n  • + Increased cloud API usage\n\nPhase 4: $2,257/month\n  • + Kubernetes cluster\n  • + Vault\n  • + Splunk",
